                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="What is your life like outside the office?"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-05-04T17:52:38.036-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="SCHAFSM"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>I’m an avid sci-fi reader. I have read the Lord of Rings books more times than I can count and over time, have enjoyed discovering new authors. I spend lots of time with my family and enjoy long bike rides and seeing what is out there. I’ll bring my phone on these rides but only to take photos.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>There is a lot of life going on. I’m not going to miss it.&lt;/p>&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
